org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.behaviours

Class DateTokenBehaviour

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.behaviours.DateTokenBehaviour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Behaviour<NiDateCell>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IndicatorDateTokenBehaviour

    public class DateTokenBehaviour
extends java.lang.Object
implements Behaviour<NiDateCell>
    the behaviour of a DateCell-populated column. These columns have no trail cells. One notable thing about their behaviour is that, upon horizontally reducing multiple DateCell instances into a NiDateCell one, the dates are displayed in chronological order.
